New in the last version:
""""""""""""""""""""""""
 - NVDICONF.CPX supports now NVDI 2.0 (meens you can toogle the Line-A
                    switcher).
 - COOKIE.CPX, SYSTEM.CPX optimations in REDRAW.
 - FILEINFO.CPX           some small changes and optimations.

New in this version:
""""""""""""""""""""
 -FILEINFO.CPX  pop-up menus handling corrected. Press and holding mouse
                button works now. Selection unpress mouse button.
 -SYSTEM.CPX    pop-up menus handling corrected.
                Extended discription and and data type (BIT).
 -NVDICONF.CPX  Must be rename, because a offical version of NVDICONF
                with the same CPX-ID is registered.
                The new name is CONFNVDI.CPX, CPX-ID: 'nVdi'. Please don't
                use the old version (NVDICONF.CPX, 'NVDI', (c) D.Fiebelkorn)
